1000004800170@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Synonymy and polysemy are fundamental problems in ⌊>natural language processing>⌋:@@@@1@10@@oe@26-8-2013
1000004800180@unknown@formal@none@1@S@⌊•⌊#Synonymy is the phenomenon where different words describe the same idea.@@@@1@11@@oe@26-8-2013
1000004800190@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Thus, a query in a search engine may fail to retrieve a relevant document that does not contain the words which appeared in the query.@@@@1@25@@oe@26-8-2013
