1000004800610@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Likewise, the only part of ⌊×V^T×⌋ that contributes to ⌊×\\textbf{d}_j×⌋ is the ⌊×j\\textrm{'th}×⌋ column, ⌊×\\hat \\textrm{d}_j×⌋.@@@@1@16@@oe@26-8-2013
