1000004800650@unknown@formal@none@1@S@The vector ⌊×\\hat \\textbf{t}_i×⌋ then has ⌊×k×⌋ entries, each giving the occurrence of term ⌊×i×⌋ in one of the ⌊×k×⌋ concepts.@@@@1@21@@oe@26-8-2013
1000004800660@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Likewise, the vector ⌊×\\hat \\textbf{d}_j×⌋ gives the relation between document ⌊×j×⌋ and each concept.@@@@1@14@@oe@26-8-2013
