1000004800700@unknown@formal@none@1@S@⌊•⌊#See how related documents ⌊×j×⌋ and ⌊×q×⌋ are in the concept space by comparing the vectors ⌊×\\hat \\textbf{d}_j×⌋ and ⌊×\\hat \\textbf{d}_q×⌋ (typically by ⌊>cosine similarity>⌋).@@@@1@25@@oe@26-8-2013
