1000004900010@unknown@formal@none@1@S@⌊δLexical categoryδ⌋@@@@1@2@@oe@26-8-2013
1000004900020@unknown@formal@none@1@S@In ⌊>grammar>⌋, a ⌊∗lexical category∗⌋ (also ⌊∗word class∗⌋, ⌊∗lexical class∗⌋, or in traditional grammar ⌊∗part of speech∗⌋) is a linguistic category of words (or more precisely ⌊/lexical items/⌋), which is generally defined by the ⌊>syntactic>⌋ or ⌊>morphological>⌋ behaviour of the lexical item in question.@@@@1@44@@oe@26-8-2013
